Alomo Bitters is a herbal based alcoholic drink produced in Ghana by Kasapreko. It is popular not only in Ghana but also in Nigeria. Its popularity has led to a lot of counterfeit production.
However, Kasapreko company took proactive measures to battle counterfeiting by introducing new bottles for the 200ml and 750ml sizes plus a tamper proof seal. Alomo Bitters now wears a premium and refreshing look.
